&lt;h2 id="installing-plakar">Installing plakar&lt;/h2>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Install &lt;strong>plakar&lt;/strong>:&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ go install github.com/PlakarKorp/plakar@v1.0.2
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>To verify the installation was successful, run:&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ plakar version
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">v1.0.2
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>

