 Requisites
 &lt;/summary>
 &lt;div class="box-content">
 &lt;p>At the time of this writing, we do not yet provide packages and &lt;strong>plakar&lt;/strong> has to be compiled from source, which requires the Go toolchain to be installed on your system.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>